data.text:
Letters received by Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham from friends, including Edward Garnett and John Masefield, following their receipt of the posthumously published 'Rhymes from a world unknown', by Gabrielle Cunninghame Graham., 1908., Acc.11335/143. Correspondence, notes, literary papers and other papers of the Cunninghame Graham family, mostly of Robert Bontine Cunninghame Graham; and financial and administrative papers relating to Gartmore and Ardoch., Acc.11335/1-227. National Library of Scotland Archives and Manuscripts Division.
